### 0. 회원가입 (테스트 계정 생성)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "name": "{{name}}",
  "birthDate": "{{birthDate}}",
  "role": "{{role}}"
}

### 0. 로그인 (토큰 발급)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}


