> {%
client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}


### 1. 강좌 개설 신청 (PENDING)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/courses
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "name": "Java Programming Basic",
  "courseType": "MANDATORY",
  "maxCapacity": 30,
  "tuition": 150000,
  "subjectId": 10,
  "academicYearId": 1,
  "teacherDetailId": 1001,
  "timeSlots": [
    {
      "dayOfWeek": "MON",
      "period": 1,
      "classroom": "Room 101"
    },
    {
      "dayOfWeek": "WED",
      "period": 2,
      "classroom": "Room 101"
    }
  ]
}

### 2. 강좌 승인 (PENDING -> OPEN)
# Course ID를 실제 생성된 ID로 변경하여 테스트하세요.
POST {{host}}/api/v1/courses/1/approve
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 3. 강좌 반려 (PENDING -> REFUSE)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/courses/2/refuse?reason=Curriculum+Insufficient
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 4. 강좌 목록 조회 (관리자 - 전체)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/courses?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 5. 강좌 목록 조회 (교사별)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/courses/teacher/200?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 6. 강좌 상태 수동 변경 (OPEN -> CLOSED)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/courses/1/status?status=CLOSED
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 7. 교사 주간 시간표 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/courses/teacher/200/timetable?semester=1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 8. 강좌 변경 요청 (정원 증가)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/courses/1/request-update?reason=Capacity+Increase
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "maxCapacity": 50,
  "tuition": 150000
}

### 9. 강좌 변경 요청 승인
# Request ID를 실제 생성된 ID로 변경하세요.
POST {{host}}/api/v1/courses/requests/1/approve
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 10. 강좌 변경 요청 반려
POST {{host}}/api/v1/courses/requests/1/reject?reason=No+Budget
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 11. 담당 교사 변경
POST {{host}}/api/v1/courses/1/change-teacher?newTeacherId=201
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 12. 강좌 폐강 (관리자 삭제)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/courses/1/cancel?reason=Low+Enrollment
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 13. 수강생 상세 조회
GET {{host}}/api/v1/courses/1/students/50
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 14. 수강생 메모 수정
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/courses/1/students/50/memo
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

학생이 수업 태도가 매우 우수함.

### 15. 수강생 강제 취소
POST {{host}}/api/v1/courses/1/students/50/force-cancel?reason=Attendance+Issue
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
